MercadoLibre,is,an,e,commerce,platform,for,Latin,American,countries,The,platform,covers,all,aspects,of,online,retail,including,building,an,online,store,offering,a,range,of,products,and,services,for,sale,advertising,those,products,and,services,and,sending,and,receiving,payments,online,MercadoLibre,offers,a,RESTful,API,for,integrating,the,various,aspects,of,its,platform,into,custom,applications